Title: Fix crash in some check previews during discovery
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1605274944
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0b1

Some check plugins crashed due to missing external information (such as host name) when trying to render the service preview during discovery.
Amongst the error messages shown in the service output are "Service description has not been set" and "Host name has not been set".
